{
  "stem": "26609.14",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as she told me this, that when happened that the Polish woman, [NON-ENGLISH] was her name, said, look, now as they went after you-- and all night I told her this story.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, you have to go out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was in the morning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I went out on the street, my child was crying.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I couldn't go even to kiss her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She said out, out, go out, because they will kill us all if you stay here longer.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Just go out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then they will send you-- from the streets, they surround people walking on the street.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Anyone walking on the streets, they took them, if they didn't work at home.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then when it happened, I had-- they surrounded us, and took us a group of people among non-Jews.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Maybe were some Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I have no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They took us to another place where we had to stay for about two or three days, I remember, until they had enough people for a transport.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We had to be about 800,000 people to send to Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "From time to time, they had to get such a number of people and send to all different parts of Germany.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that's why I said before that we had to go through an officer, and that Ukrainian helped me, the person behind the desk who gave us all documents to go to Germany to be sent to Germany.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I rem--",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
